The evidence with the title 'Q&A with Amtrak president Alex Kummant | Reuters ' says Jun 12, 2008  ... Two years ago we grew a little more than 1 percent ridership . Last year 6.3 percent and this year we believe certainly ridership will grow north of 10 percent and  ... We could easily spend twice of that if you look at the state of the repair backlog .  ... And the answer is if you have $ 40 billion we will talk about it'. 
